---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="Install / Getting Started">
  <section>
    <h2>Install & build guide</h2>

    <p class="lead">This guide shows how to run Quick Log locally and how to build Android release artifacts.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Flutter SDK 3.10.1 or higher</li>
        <li>Dart 3.10.1 or higher</li>
        <li>Java 17+ (for Android builds)</li>
        <li>Android Studio or Android SDK (API 21+)</li>
        <li>Node 18+ (for the website, not required for the app)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Clone the repository</h3>
      <pre style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);padding:10px;border-radius:8px;overflow:auto">git clone https://github.com/cmwen/quick-log-app.git
cd quick-log-app</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Run locally</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Get dependencies: <code>flutter pub get</code></li>
        <li>Run on an Android device/emulator: <code>flutter run</code></li>
      </ol>
      <pre style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);padding:10px;border-radius:8px;overflow:auto">flutter run

# List devices (useful when multiple are connected)
flutter devices</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Build release artifacts</h3>
      <pre style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);padding:10px;border-radius:8px;overflow:auto">flutter build apk         # Android APK
flutter build appbundle   # Play Store (AAB)</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Run tests</h3>
      <pre style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);padding:10px;border-radius:8px;overflow:auto">flutter test              # Run all tests
flutter test --coverage   # With coverage</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Website (optional)</h3>
      <p>If you need to work on the repository website, switch to the <code>astro/</code> directory and run:</p>
      <pre style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);padding:10px;border-radius:8px;overflow:auto">cd astro
npm install
npm run dev</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Need more help?</h3>
      <p>Start with <a href="https://github.com/cmwen/quick-log-app/blob/main/GETTING_STARTED.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">GETTING_STARTED.md</a> and <a href="https://github.com/cmwen/quick-log-app/blob/main/QUICK_LOG_README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">QUICK_LOG_README.md</a>.</p>
      <p>For CI or release setup, check <code>.github/workflows/</code>. To report issues, use the <a href="https://github.com/cmwen/quick-log-app/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">issue tracker</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
